* if you want to filter of dropdown instead of textbox in grid view, then write this in gridColumn

[
	'attribute' => 'status',
	'filter' => ['on' => 'On', 'off' => 'Off'],
	'filterInputOptions' => [
					'prompt' => 'status',		
				],
]

* if you want to set placeholder in textfield of gridview then,

[
	'attribute' => 'status',
	'filterInputOptions' => [
					'placeholder' => 'status',
				],
]
